channel.title: Matik - Kicoh (XIEJRA REMIX) [Orchestral Drumstep]
channel.description:
Hey i’m back with another remix! For @Matik and his remix competition, Took so long to do this because I left it for a while and I couldn’t figure out what to do for a drop.
Not my best I must say, but netherless I gave it my all ;) Anyway I hope you enjoy this, n wish me luck :)
Listen here: https://soundcloud.com/xiejramusic/matik-kicoh-xiejra-remix
